author: Leah Garchik
title: World champion Warriors take BART back to Oakland
text:
President Obama at the Warfield President Obama at the Warfield
Waiting for a train to Oakland on the Civic Center BART platform the day President Obama was at the Warfield, Jim Martinsen saw the members of the Warriors, waiting for the train, too. The theater was surrounded by security. After weighing all the departure options, including limos, it had been determined that the quickest way for the players to get back to Oakland was by BART.
